00:02:09.296 --> 00:02:13.174
OPASNOST IZ DUBINE

00:02:25.479 --> 00:02:27.063
MAMA 1991.

00:02:27.147 --> 00:02:29.065
MEKSIKO

00:02:29.149 --> 00:02:31.484
MAMA 1991.

00:02:40.410 --> 00:02:42.078
To si ti na plaži?

00:02:42.162 --> 00:02:43.454
Ne, to je moja mama.

00:02:44.665 --> 00:02:47.375
Došla je ovamo saznavši
da je trudna sa mnom.

00:02:47.459 --> 00:02:51.003
Ja nisam nikad bila,
no to je naša plaža.

00:02:57.010 --> 00:02:58.302
To je moja sestrica.

00:03:05.102 --> 00:03:06.853
Želiš li vidjeti još slika?

00:03:13.277 --> 00:03:15.069
Samo za tvoje oči.

00:03:15.153 --> 00:03:16.571
Prava. Autentična.

00:03:16.655 --> 00:03:17.864
Imaš pravo.

00:03:17.948 --> 00:03:18.990
Hvala ti.

00:03:20.659 --> 00:03:22.159
Oprosti. Amerikanka sam.

00:03:23.620 --> 00:03:25.454
Ovdje nema mnogo gringosa.

00:03:25.539 --> 00:03:26.831
Da, smola.

00:03:37.217 --> 00:03:39.427
Neću stići na plažu.
Vrti mi se.

00:03:39.511 --> 00:03:40.720
Ona ne dolazi?

00:03:40.971 --> 00:03:41.762
Tko?

00:03:41.847 --> 00:03:43.472
Moja prijateljica. Mi amiga.

00:03:44.558 --> 00:03:46.142
Cura koja je ostala u hotelu.

00:03:46.226 --> 00:03:48.060
Miriše na Don Julia...

00:03:48.145 --> 00:03:49.729
i loš izbor.

00:03:49.813 --> 00:03:51.105
Uvijek mi to radi.

00:03:51.189 --> 00:03:52.648
Samo nestane.

00:03:52.733 --> 00:03:54.400
Ona je kao fantasmo.

00:03:54.484 --> 00:03:55.776
Znaš što je fantasmo?

00:03:55.861 --> 00:03:58.237
<i>-Fantasma. Sa "A."
-Da, s "A."</i>

00:03:58.322 --> 00:04:00.781
Razlog zašto sam
planirala ovo putovanje,

00:04:00.866 --> 00:04:02.450
bio je da nađem tajnu plažu.

00:04:02.534 --> 00:04:05.369
Ona je sad u Las Rocasu,
ima irsku gripu.

00:04:07.873 --> 00:04:09.832
Liječi mamurnost.

00:04:12.502 --> 00:04:15.046
Veliku mamurnost.

00:04:15.797 --> 00:04:18.674
Profesionalno, mislim
da trebaš uzeti 2 Advila.

00:04:18.759 --> 00:04:21.552
Ne voliš kad netko
promijeni tvoje planove?

00:04:21.637 --> 00:04:22.887
Ne, ne volim.

00:04:22.971 --> 00:04:24.472
Ne, ne volim. To nije...

00:04:24.556 --> 00:04:25.640
To nije pravedno.

00:04:25.724 --> 00:04:26.891
Znaš li zašto?

00:04:26.975 --> 00:04:28.309
Zato što sam ja pouzdana.

00:04:28.393 --> 00:04:30.311
Znaš što to znači?

00:04:31.396 --> 00:04:33.147
Šefuješ.

00:04:34.775 --> 00:04:36.817
Ja sam pouzdana.

00:04:38.236 --> 00:04:39.487
Da, šefuješ.

00:04:40.989 --> 00:04:42.239
Takva sam.

00:04:42.324 --> 00:04:44.200
Jako volim šefovati.

00:04:50.415 --> 00:04:51.999
Dobru zabavu! Vidimo se!

00:04:52.084 --> 00:04:55.378
Saznala si ime tajne plaže?

00:04:55.462 --> 00:04:56.837
Kako se zove ova plaža?

00:04:59.383 --> 00:05:01.717
Nećeš mi reći. Cool.

00:05:02.761 --> 00:05:03.886
<i>Cool. Frio.</i>

00:05:03.971 --> 00:05:05.388
<i>Yo tengo frio.</i>

00:05:05.472 --> 00:05:06.847
Nemoguće.

00:05:06.932 --> 00:05:08.391
Ovdje je prevruće.

00:05:08.475 --> 00:05:10.559
Ne, ti si cool.

00:05:10.644 --> 00:05:12.186
Nema veze, u redu je.

00:05:13.397 --> 00:05:14.480
Shvaćam.

00:05:28.662 --> 00:05:29.870
To je ta?

00:06:15.208 --> 00:06:16.333
Ovo je raj.

00:06:17.461 --> 00:06:20.087
Savršeno.

00:06:27.012 --> 00:06:30.723
Ovo je otok trudne žene...

00:06:30.807 --> 00:06:31.557
Ne?

00:06:32.768 --> 00:06:33.726
Ne.

00:06:33.810 --> 00:06:34.935
Da...

00:06:35.020 --> 00:06:39.440
Nos... dojke... I njezin trbuh.

00:06:39.524 --> 00:06:41.025
Ne.

00:06:43.445 --> 00:06:45.988
Da, za mene jest.

00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:07.635
-Ne, ne. Molim te.
-Ne, molim te.

00:07:07.719 --> 00:07:08.719
Molim te, ustrajem.

00:07:08.804 --> 00:07:10.221
Ne, išli smo u istom smjeru.

00:07:10.305 --> 00:07:12.306
Živim blizu. Ne brini se.

00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:13.891
Sigurno?

00:07:13.975 --> 00:07:16.936
-Da.
-Hvala ti.

00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:18.813
I drugi put.

00:07:19.481 --> 00:07:20.397
Ja sam Nancy.

00:07:20.482 --> 00:07:23.192
-Carlos. Charlie.
-Drago mi je, Charlie.

00:07:23.276 --> 00:07:24.193
Također.

00:07:26.071 --> 00:07:27.780
Srednja škola.

00:07:27.864 --> 00:07:29.156
Ideš u srednju?

00:07:29.241 --> 00:07:30.241
Ne.

00:07:30.325 --> 00:07:33.202
Bila sam na medicini,
ali nismo učili španjolski,

00:07:33.286 --> 00:07:36.455
samo o truplima. Ušutjet ću.

00:07:36.540 --> 00:07:38.582
Za koji sat će mrak, pa...

00:07:38.667 --> 00:07:40.543
Nikad ne surfam noću.

00:07:40.627 --> 00:07:43.754
Kako ćeš otići odavde?

00:07:43.839 --> 00:07:45.172
Uberom.

00:07:45.257 --> 00:07:46.799
Tko je Uber?

00:07:47.676 --> 00:07:49.176
Nema veze. Hvala, Carlose,

00:07:49.261 --> 00:07:51.053
što si me dovezao.

00:07:51.138 --> 00:07:53.347
To mi mnogo znači.

00:07:53.431 --> 00:07:57.601
Kako si ono rekao da se zove?
Zbog nečega sam zaboravila.

00:07:57.686 --> 00:07:59.228
Oprezno.

00:07:59.813 --> 00:08:00.646
Uvijek.

00:08:30.010 --> 00:08:31.051
OPREMA ZA SURFANJE

00:08:31.136 --> 00:08:32.636
KREMA ZA SUNČANJE

00:11:19.429 --> 00:11:20.804
Hej!

00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:29.438
Govoriti španjolski, guera?

00:11:35.904 --> 00:11:37.863
Ne razumijem. Žao mi je.

00:11:37.947 --> 00:11:40.324
Kaže da je teško
veslati protiv struje.

00:11:40.408 --> 00:11:41.867
Da, nisam to očekivala.

00:11:41.951 --> 00:11:44.453
Gotovo me povukla natrag.

00:11:46.623 --> 00:11:47.831
Amerikanka?

00:11:47.916 --> 00:11:50.793
Da, Amerikanka.

00:11:51.711 --> 00:11:52.920
Kalifornija?

00:11:53.963 --> 00:11:55.381
Blizu. Teksas.

00:11:56.341 --> 00:11:58.008
U Teksasu surfaju?

00:11:58.093 --> 00:12:01.512
Da, možemo surfati.
No nije ovako.

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:10.938
Ovo je tajno mjesto.
Kako si ga pronašla?

00:12:11.022 --> 00:12:14.233
Netko mi je davno rekao.
Kako se zove?

00:12:14.317 --> 00:12:16.985
Ako ti kažem,
morat ću te ubiti!

00:12:17.904 --> 00:12:19.613
To bi mi upropastilo dan.

00:12:20.657 --> 00:12:23.117
Ima li čega opasnog
za što moram znati?

00:12:23.201 --> 00:12:24.827
Ondje ima stijena!

00:12:24.911 --> 00:12:26.954
Samo je jedna plima u danu,

00:12:27.038 --> 00:12:29.331
a kad je oseka,
postanu otok.

00:12:29.416 --> 00:12:31.667
Ima vatrenih koralja.

00:12:31.751 --> 00:12:34.044
Opeku kao meduza.

00:12:34.129 --> 00:12:35.754
U redu!

00:12:44.681 --> 00:12:47.141
I dalje nemam pojma što govoriš.

00:12:48.226 --> 00:12:50.227
Kaže da trebaš doći ovamo.

00:12:50.311 --> 00:12:52.563
Valovi su bolji.

00:12:52.647 --> 00:12:55.441
U redu je.
Cool mi je ovdje. Hvala.

00:12:55.525 --> 00:12:57.693
<i>Oprezno, gringa.</i>

00:12:57.777 --> 00:13:00.654
Ovdje je gadno
za curicu iz Teksasa.

00:13:00.738 --> 00:13:02.739
Mislim da ću biti dobro.

00:14:37.377 --> 00:14:38.585
To!

00:16:10.928 --> 00:16:12.012
Zovem Malu

00:16:12.096 --> 00:16:13.639
<i>-Mala?
-Hej!</i>

00:16:14.515 --> 00:16:15.932
<i>-Pogodi gdje sam.
-Tijuana.</i>

00:16:18.603 --> 00:16:20.395
<i>O, Bože. Ni govora.</i>

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:21.521
<i>Mamina plaža, zar ne?</i>

00:16:21.606 --> 00:16:23.565
Lijepa je kako je rekla.

00:16:24.859 --> 00:16:27.110
Da si bar ovdje.

00:16:27.195 --> 00:16:28.570
I da je ona ovdje.

00:16:28.655 --> 00:16:30.989
<i>Znači li to... da si sama?</i>

00:16:31.074 --> 00:16:34.993
Nisam došla ovamo u strahu
jer sam izgubila partnericu.

00:16:35.078 --> 00:16:37.621
<i>Tako završiš
kod Nancy Grace.</i>

00:16:38.373 --> 00:16:41.416
Pardon! Ja trebam biti
dosadna prezaštitnička sestra!

00:16:41.501 --> 00:16:43.085
Ti trebaš biti zabavna.

00:16:43.836 --> 00:16:45.921
Seko, valovi su ovdje ludi.

00:16:46.005 --> 00:16:48.507
Da znaš kakvu sam
savršenu cijev uhvatila.

00:16:48.591 --> 00:16:52.469
<i>Ja ih mogu odvesti dobro
kao i ti, samo da me povedeš!</i>

00:16:52.553 --> 00:16:53.679
Povest ću te.

00:16:53.763 --> 00:16:55.305
Čim se vratim.

00:16:56.224 --> 00:16:57.724
<i>Volim te, seko-mama.</i>

00:16:57.809 --> 00:16:59.559
<i>-I ja tebe.
-To je Nancy?</i>

00:16:59.644 --> 00:17:01.186
-Tata.
-Reci mu da sam dobro.

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:02.604
<i>-Volim te. Bok.
-Ne, prijateljica je.</i>

00:17:02.689 --> 00:17:03.939
<i>Nance, ne prekidaj.</i>

00:17:04.023 --> 00:17:05.482
<i>Daj telefon. Chloe.</i>

00:17:06.150 --> 00:17:07.067
<i>Hej!</i>

00:17:07.151 --> 00:17:08.402
Hej, tata.

00:17:08.486 --> 00:17:09.444
<i>Hej, slatkice.</i>

00:17:09.529 --> 00:17:10.904
<i>Gdje si?</i>

00:17:10.988 --> 00:17:12.406
U Meksiku.

00:17:13.408 --> 00:17:15.867
<i>Ne znam što da kažem.
Nemam riječi.</i>

00:17:15.952 --> 00:17:18.453
<i>-Ne mogu shvatiti...
-I ne očekujem.</i>

00:17:18.538 --> 00:17:19.871
<i>Onda mi pomogni.</i>

00:17:19.956 --> 00:17:22.249
Ne znam. Što hoćeš da kažem?

00:17:22.333 --> 00:17:23.375
<i>Reci da se vraćaš.</i>

00:17:23.459 --> 00:17:27.212
<i>Reci da se vraćaš, da ne odustaješ od
medicine nakon toliko vremena i rada.</i>

00:17:27.296 --> 00:17:29.256
<i>-Samo ne odustaj.
-Dobro, tata.</i>

00:17:29.340 --> 00:17:32.092
Dosta je. Nemojmo sad o tome.

00:17:32.176 --> 00:17:33.844
<i>To voliš.
Pomažeš ljudima.</i>

00:17:33.928 --> 00:17:35.512
Ne može se svakomu pomoći.

00:17:35.596 --> 00:17:36.805
Znaš to.

00:17:36.889 --> 00:17:38.223
<i>Ne radi to.</i>

00:17:39.350 --> 00:17:40.434
<i>Nemoj da je zbog nje.</i>

00:17:40.518 --> 00:17:42.018
Nego zbog koga bi bilo?

00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:47.357
<i>Ako tako želiš,
ostani na studiju.</i>

00:17:47.442 --> 00:17:48.942
<i>Ona je bila borac.</i>

00:17:52.989 --> 00:17:55.365
Samo se previše borila.

00:17:56.325 --> 00:17:58.410
Znaš? A za što?

00:18:00.121 --> 00:18:01.580
Završilo je isto.

00:18:03.082 --> 00:18:05.292
<i>Samo se vrati, Nancy.</i>

00:18:05.376 --> 00:18:06.793
<i>Molim te.</i>

00:18:08.045 --> 00:18:09.921
Moram ići. Vidimo se uskoro.

00:18:10.006 --> 00:18:11.006
<i>Kad?</i>

00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:12.966
<i>-Kad?
-Ne znam.</i>

00:18:13.050 --> 00:18:14.050
<i>Nance.</i>

00:18:15.094 --> 00:18:16.386
Volim te. Bok.

00:18:36.157 --> 00:18:41.536
Naći ću se sa zgodnim
od sinoć!! Ne čekaj me!

